HEADWORD: Gladiole
<hw>Glad"i*ole</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>gladiolus</ets> a small sword, the sword lily, dim. of
<ets>gladius</ets> sword. See <er>Glaive</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A lilylike plant, of the genus <gen>Gladiolus</gen>; -- called also
<altname>corn flag</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gladiolus</ent>⟦br⟧
